This documentation describes the topic: https://material.angular.io/guide/creating-a-custom-form-field-control

This:
```ts
@Component({
  ...
  providers: [{provide: MatFormFieldControl, useExisting: MyTelInput}],
})
class MyTelInput implements MatFormFieldControl<MyTel> {
  ...
}
```
Should be:
```ts
@Component({
  ...
})
class MyTelInput extends MatFormFieldControl<MyTel> {
  ...
}
```

This:
```ts
@Input()
get placeholder() {
  return this._placeholder;
}
set placeholder(plh) {
  this._placeholder = plh;
  this.stateChanges.next();
}
private _placeholder: string;
```
```html
<input [placeholder]="_placeholder">
```
Should be:
```ts
@Input() placeholder: string
```
```html
<input [placeholder]="placeholder">
```

And so on...
